{"tid":542393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"ACL 同半月板撕裂 做手術一問","createTime":"2018-01-27T12:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T07:31:57.000Z","uid":169093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ebfcbac6bb40c5418ca277ec49eb498308ee34c1","tid":542393,"uid":169093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"小弟熱愛打波 但期間整親過幾次膝頭哥 每次睇左跌打搽野消腫就以為冇事<br />\n最近轉玩羽毛球 執波起身果下聽到啪一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  膝頭依舊同以前腫加痛 把心一橫去照磁力共振<br />\n點知醫生話 ACL 加半月板撕裂 後者仲捲起埋 手術就走唔甩 比左封轉介信封我<br />\n想問有冇巴打聽過類似經驗 私院貴到hihi 有冇邊個公立醫院既骨科係好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef89564a2837e96aac239b60ebf4c16084903b6","tid":542393,"uid":689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"自己私院做"},{"pid":"0b516b9be7a6cb8a482ccb785a4045ffbc501b03","tid":542393,"uid":169093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe5cce29ea96fd750eab2956c75c26d5b1125e1","tid":542393,"uid":96358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"港島囉 <br />\n<br />\n其實都係睇彩數 基本上做得手術班醫生唔會比私院差 只係等得耐，住既環境冇咁好姐"},{"pid":"2af368feaec4fa2922fe0a36f0324f7d7ec602c9","tid":542393,"uid":96358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"不過你傷埋半月板 你個手術前rehab要做得好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n預返手術後一頭半個月隻腳唔食得力咁 d肌肉縮哂咁"},{"pid":"dc91c30655e57d08c270c97bfec95d8d388ae74d","tid":542393,"uid":167166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"有無買保險？私院做會快好多<br />\n最重要係做完手術之後既物理治療"},{"pid":"a40bd18aa7f23375bba9518268c10a2ccb7970da","tid":542393,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"利申: ACL+半月板撕裂過來人，症狀同你一樣，而且直頭行唔到路<br />\n<br />\n之前去公家話要照MRI，結果要排兩年，手術排期就唔清楚，但等MRI真心耐到痴撚線。所以當時果斷去私家，day1照完，day2做手術。建議你真係去私家好過。長時間行唔到路，生活質素真係會好差。"},{"pid":"bd9ce1d7d953429a50aa84c9ba46932904f62a9e","tid":542393,"uid":96358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:55:06.000Z","msg":"補充下 公立手術排期 6個月至一年到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：ACL斷左，rehab緊，但我排左兩個月就做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0110c5675af9b258839eb4e69e660ef01824af37","tid":542393,"uid":4316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"過來人，斷左ACL同半月板撕裂晒<br />\n<br />\n我係你就去私院做，唔好慳果小小錢<br />\n<br />\n始終隻腳跟自己一世<br />\n<br />\n果時由斷，到轉介去照MRI，再到做手術前後等左成年<br />\n<br />\n到呢家隻腳仲未完全好返晒，好易會攰同酸軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076108c85a60d501a6b94658acc99a0117567148","tid":542393,"uid":127894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"公立排照MRI 要排兩年以上囉 <br />\n最後去左私家照 兩個膝頭收左我一萬 <br />\n照完醫生話對膝乜事都無 好彩"},{"pid":"0048fd7fb0edabaf7a37047c7b1b8523a372ed42","tid":542393,"uid":169093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2af368feaec4fa2922fe0a36f0324f7d7ec602c9","tid":542393,"uid":96358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"不過你傷埋半月板 你個手術前rehab要做得好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n預返手術後一頭半個月隻腳唔食得力咁 d肌肉縮哂咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"你又咁好彩咁快排到 瑪麗做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e1631dbda8a5ebd303152e93bfe65e012e4238","tid":542393,"uid":169093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0110c5675af9b258839eb4e69e660ef01824af37","tid":542393,"uid":4316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"過來人，斷左ACL同半月板撕裂晒<br />\n<br />\n我係你就去私院做，唔好慳果小小錢<br />\n<br />\n始終隻腳跟自己一世<br />\n<br />\n果時由斷，到轉介去照MRI，再到做手術前後等左成年<br />\n<br />\n到呢家隻腳仲未完全好返晒，好易會攰同酸軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"如果有買保險當然想私家做 但家在公屋 屋企人覺得買保險係徒錢 唔肯比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e6c94e0be4b21fb3a2fe5d1b934a5a7af2dc02","tid":542393,"uid":4316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7e1631dbda8a5ebd303152e93bfe65e012e4238","tid":542393,"uid":169093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0110c5675af9b258839eb4e69e660ef01824af37","tid":542393,"uid":4316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"過來人，斷左ACL同半月板撕裂晒<br />\n<br />\n我係你就去私院做，唔好慳果小小錢<br />\n<br />\n始終隻腳跟自己一世<br />\n<br />\n果時由斷，到轉介去照MRI，再到做手術前後等左成年<br />\n<br />\n到呢家隻腳仲未完全好返晒，好易會攰同酸軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"如果有買保險當然想私家做 但家在公屋 屋企人覺得買保險係徒錢 唔肯比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}